-- Simon Property Said to Add Four Backers to General Growth Investment Plan
-- Daniel Taub
-- 2010-04-21T22:02:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/simon-property-said-to-add-four-backers-to-general-growth-investment-plan.html

          
          
             Simon Property Group Inc. added
four backers to its investment plan for General Growth
Properties Inc., bringing the mall owner’s total offer to $4.6
billion, according to a person familiar with the proposal.  
 The investors joining the bid are Taconic Capital Advisors,
Oak Hill Advisors LP, ING Clarion and RREEF, said the person,
who asked not to be named because the plan hasn’t been made
public.   
